  "title": "PERM NIGHT SHIFT Pharmacist ( Private Hospital 8pm - 8am )  #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Dispense prescription and over-the-counter medications</li>\n  <li>Advise patients on proper medication use and potential side effects</li>\n  <li>Verify and review prescription orders for accuracy</li>\n  <li>Maintain patient records and ensure confidentiality</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with healthcare providers to enhance patient care</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s Degree in Pharmacy or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Registered Pharmacist with the Singapore Pharmacy Council</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p>\n<p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
